               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the scribe and donor(s); groups of lines in the
                        incipit page of Texts I-1 and I-4; incipit of all other texts, incipit of
                        sections of texts; abbreviated form of the word ʾesäggǝd "I worship" in Text
                        I-3; elements of the punctuation signs and of the text dividers; elements of
                        Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Most of the miracles of Mary (Text I-4) are numbered.</note>
                     <note>The first miracle of Michael (Text III) is followed by an
                        ʾarke-hymn.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1">
                     <colophon>
                        <locus/>Fol.
                        94vb: ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአፈጸመኒ፡ ዘንተ፡ ተአምረ፡ በደኅና፡ ወበሰላም፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፰ለግንቦት፡ ፲ወ፫ሠርቀ፡
                        ሌሊት፡ ዘመነ፡ ማርቆስ። በ፲፻ወ፱፻ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት።<foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                        <note>The writing was completed on the 13th of Gǝnbot in the year of mercy
                           1900 (= 21.05.1908 A.D).</note>
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
